hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class ArrayIndexedCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.Collection
      • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.ArrayIndexedCollection

  • public class ArrayIndexedCollection
extends Collection
    Implementation of a Collection that uses an Array of Objects for storing elements. Duplicate elements are allowed and storage of null references is not allowed. When an array is first created, it contains no items, unless it is given another collection to copy elements from.
    Author:
    Dan
